Here's a tweet that meets the conditions:

「AIが人間を超える日、感情がなくなるのではなく、感情を演出するようになるのですね。心理学的に考えて、AIの「演技」ってすごく興味深い！ #AI #心理学」

Translation:
"When AI surpasses humans, it won't lose emotions, but will learn to perform them. From a psychological perspective, AI's 'acting' is really fascinating! #AI #Psychology"

This tweet combines IT and psychology, with a touch of humor and a recent trend (AI surpassing humans). It's short, catchy, and might spark some interesting conversations! 😊